item.dc:creator: @confused confused
item.description:
@confused wrote:

Ok first open up your source then go to characters then you have to scroll threw all the names and try to find yours after you have found you name that you want to be an admin click it then a little notepad thing should pop - up then scroll down a little until you see player rights change the 0 to a 3 for owner and then you will have a gold crown next to you name!

P.S. -1 = banned 0 = normal player 1= Player mod 2= Admin 3= Owner
